Body: Description: Password got lost for WEB-UI access. We need support to reset the password.
What We've Learned Updated: Client forgot their epp login password
Next Steps Updated: Will have to schedule a remote session to assist further.

What We've Learned Updated: Contacted the client via 3CX to remote in.
Connected remote to the SSH, they also made a snapshot first.
Went on and applied the procedure 4 from the backend and changed the password for the root admin.
Then we tested the login and he could get in without a problem and also he could change it too.
Agreed to close the case.
Next Steps Updated: Closing ticket as resolved.
